 variable 
\family typewriter
NCPUS
\family default
 to an integer will inform 
\emph on
multiafnmr.sh
\emph default
 to process the given number of structures simultaneously.
 This is primarily useful when using the -solinprot option, which takes
 longer to compute surface charges with.
\end_layout

